Brooke, performing her own song, "I Hurt."

00:33:25.536 --> 00:33:27.438 line:95%,end
Woo!

00:33:27.505 --> 00:33:28.806 line:95%,end
[applause]

00:33:28.873 --> 00:33:31.142 line:5%,start
[music playing]

00:33:39.984 --> 00:33:45.723 line:95%,end
I keep moving, going through the motions.

00:33:45.790 --> 00:33:51.529 line:95%,end
