00:34:21.759 --> 00:34:23.361 line:95%,end
[cheering]

00:34:23.428 --> 00:34:25.596 line:95%,end
Woo!

00:34:25.663 --> 00:34:27.365 line:95%,end
[cheering]

00:34:27.432 --> 00:34:29.267 line:95%,end
I'm very proud of Brooke,
under the circumstances.

00:34:29.333 --> 00:34:31.869 line:95%,end
She had 15 minutes to learn this dance.

00:34:31.936 --> 00:34:34.505 line:95%,end
She was dancing to her own song.

