00:34:41.279 --> 00:34:42.847 line:95%,end
JILL: I still want you to--

00:34:42.914 --> 00:34:44.882 line:95%,end
KELLY: G, how great-- you
guys, how great would it

00:34:44.949 --> 00:34:46.584 line:95%,end
