00:34:46.651 --> 00:34:47.785 line:95%,end
I hope so.

00:34:47.852 --> 00:34:50.755 line:95%,end
And Abby hasn't been here all week.
Abby hasn't done a single thing.

00:34:50.822 --> 00:34:52.623 line:95%,end
This would be on you and Gia.

00:34:52.690 --> 00:34:53.925 line:95%,end
And this dance is different, you guys.

00:34:53.991 --> 00:34:56.861 line:95%,end
This dance is going to be something that
they haven't seen yet today.

00:34:56.928 --> 00:34:58.362 line:95%,end
I can guarantee you that.

00:34:58.429 --> 00:35:01.899 line:95%,end
Gia, would you take all nine kids,
for a small group, to nationals?

00:35:03.067 --> 00:35:04.769 line:95%,end
Ask me again after they dance.

00:35:04.836 --> 00:35:06.037 line:95%,end
Okay. That's fair.

00:35:06.104 --> 00:35:08.139 line:5%,start
It's so important to me
today that the girls dance

00:35:08.206 --> 00:35:11.242 line:5%,start
their best, to show Abby
that I can pull this off,

00:35:11.309 --> 00:35:13.111 line:95%,end
that I can pull out a win for her team.

00:35:13.177 --> 00:35:15.446 line:95%,end
I need them to be as
strong as they ever were.

00:35:15.513 --> 00:35:17.548 line:95%,end
[music playing]

00:35:17.615 --> 00:35:19.851 line:95%,end
ANNOUNCER: Coming up next,
ladies and gentlemen,

00:35:19.917 --> 00:35:22.253 line:5%,start
is going to be entry 81.

00:35:22.320 --> 00:35:24.922 line:95%,end
Put your hands together for, "Just Be."

00:35:24.989 --> 00:35:28.826 line:95%,end
[applause]

00:35:28.893 --> 00:35:30.828 line:95%,end
[cheering]

00:35:30.895 --> 00:35:33.164 line:5%,start
[music playing]

00:35:39.704 --> 00:35:43.374 line:95%,end
Life has changes,

00:35:43.441 --> 00:35:47.512 line:95%,end
rearranges,

00:35:47.578 --> 00:35:51.482 line:95%,end
but I want this to stay.

00:35:55.386 --> 00:35:58.523 line:95%,end
We'll just be.

00:36:03.594 --> 00:36:06.964 line:95%,end
We'll just be.

00:36:11.335 --> 00:36:17.875 line:95%,end
Like two birds flying over the sea,

00:36:19.343 --> 00:36:25.917 line:95%,end
we'll just be

00:36:25.983 --> 00:36:29.453 line:95%,end
in our melody.

00:36:29.520 --> 00:36:30.788 line:95%,end
[cheering]

00:36:30.855 --> 00:36:32.723 line:95%,end
[music playing]

00:36:32.790 --> 00:36:34.058 line:95%,end
[applause]

00:36:35.726 --> 00:36:37.128 line:95%,end
Did so great.

00:36:37.195 --> 00:36:41.165 line:5%,start
It has been a long time since
I felt so emotionally invested

00:36:41.232 --> 00:36:42.333 line:95%,end
in a group dance.

00:36:42.400 --> 00:36:45.203 line:95%,end
And if these girls can pull
off a win without Abby,

00:36:45.269 --> 00:36:47.538 line:95%,end
this might be my favorite victory ever.

00:36:47.605 --> 00:36:50.041 line:5%,start
[cheering]


00:36:50.107 --> 00:36:52.610 line:5%,start
[music playing]

00:36:52.677 --> 00:36:54.879 line:95%,end
We want one.

00:36:54.946 --> 00:36:57.114 line:95%,end
All right.
We're going to start.

00:36:57.181 --> 00:37:02.920 line:5%,start
Moving into the advanced level, second
place, "Over the Rainbow."

00:37:02.987 --> 00:37:04.188 line:95%,end
[applause]

00:37:04.255 --> 00:37:08.059 line:95%,end
And your highest scoring
eight number solo

00:37:08.125 --> 00:37:10.127 line:5%,start
