00:37:10.194 --> 00:37:11.429 line:5%,start
[cheering]

00:37:11.495 --> 00:37:13.798 line:5%,start
[music playing]

00:37:13.864 --> 00:37:15.466 line:95%,end
[applause]

00:37:15.533 --> 00:37:18.436 line:5%,start
So Asia gets first, and I knew she would.

00:37:18.502 --> 00:37:19.971 line:95%,end
This solo was so her.

