My mother comes first.

00:41:13.571 --> 00:41:17.641 line:5%,start
I need the dancer that
can be Chloe this weekend.

00:41:17.708 --> 00:41:20.277 line:5%,start
Did Abby mention anything
about nationals, Melissa?

00:41:20.344 --> 00:41:21.612 line:5%,start
