- I'm listening.

00:41:21.679 --> 00:41:22.780 line:5%,start
You're the God, I know.

00:41:22.847 --> 00:41:24.315 line:5%,start
You make a point to tell all of us.

00:41:24.381 --> 00:41:27.218 line:5%,start
Tiffany, I thought you
and I were a team, adios,

00:41:27.284 --> 00:41:29.420 line:5%,start
[inaudible] get out of here.

00:41:29.487 --> 00:41:30.888 line:5%,start
Gianna, where's Abby?

